    <transientAllowed/>
    <text>Populate the allListObjects and allLevels arrays by calling
the self.addListObject method for all items you want to display.
(They will populate the list boc in sync.
The form will effectivly "return" the array with only the selected
object(s) in it.
Set the allowMultiSelect property to allow multi select</text>
